item.title: Bomb the Bridge
item.description: Plant C4 bombs anywhere on the bridge. Wait for enemy troops to cross, then detonate them. Blow up 100% of the bridge and eliminate all troops to score 3 stars. Features: Realistic physics Addictive theme Challenging levels Blow up armies, military trucks and tanks!
